cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper discusses a blockchain-based design for secure and auditable storage and sharing of IoT data. This involves access control management, decentralized storage, and data ownership. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DB (Databases), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
